    <data key="d0">Aetion: Automated Multi-Tenant SaaS Deployment Pipeline via CloudFormation</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6YkguepAQuQ</data>
    <data key="d2">Automates deployment of healthcare analytics software. Uses CloudFormation Change Sets to govern manual approvals. Deploys to up to 100 parallel VPCs for customer isolation.</data>
